<!--C#-->
<section class="text-light p-5 p-lg-0 pt-lg-5 text-center">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="d-sm-flex align-items-center justify-content-between">
            <img src="~/Image/firstIcon2.png" class="pb-4 w-25 img-fluid" />
            <div>

                <h2 class="text-warning">C#</h2>

                <p class="lead">
                    C# (C-Sharp) is a programming language developed by Microsoft that runs on the .NET Framework. C# is used to develop web apps, desktop apps, mobile apps, and other applications.
                    It was designed by Anders Hejlsberg from Microsoft in 2000 and would later be approved by international standards.
                </p>
                <a class="btn btn-info" href="https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/dotnet/csharp/">Learn More About C#</a>
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>
</section>


<!--JS-->
<section class="text-light p-5 p-lg-0 pt-lg-5 text-center">
